#: addons/notify-speed.wad/addon:2 input:9 standard
msgid "Speed Down on Notify"
msgstr ""

#: addons/notify-speed.wad/addon:3 input:6 standard
msgid ""
"Reduce the game speed to 1× whenever a new message arrives in your inbox."
msgstr ""

#: addons/notify-speed.wad/init.lua:15 input:15 standard
msgid "Speed Down on Notify Disabled"
msgstr ""

#: addons/notify-speed.wad/init.lua:15 input:15 standard
msgid "Speed Down on Notify Enabled"
msgstr ""

#: addons/notify-speed.wad/init.lua:17 input:17 standard
msgid ""
"The game will from now on be sped down to 1× speed whenever a new inbox "
"message arrives. You can disable ‘Speed Down on Notify’ mode by using the "
"toolbar button again."
msgstr ""

#: addons/notify-speed.wad/init.lua:18 input:18 standard
msgid ""
"The game will no longer be sped down when a new inbox message arrives. You "
"can re-enable ‘Speed Down on Notify’ mode by using the toolbar button again."
msgstr ""

#: addons/notify-speed.wad/init.lua:41 addons/notify-speed.wad/shortcuts.lua:6
#: input:6 input:41 standard standard input:6
msgid "Toggle ‘Speed Down on Notify’ Mode"
msgstr ""

#: addons/notify-speed.wad/init.lua:42 input:42 standard
msgid ""
"Toggle whether to speed the game down when a new notification is received."
msgstr ""
